<ul><li>Detailed backframing for interior offices in progress</li>
<li>Window installation in progress</li>
<li>Plumbing, Mechanical &amp; Sprinkler work starting next week.</li>
<li>Interior atrium stair to be constructed next week.</li>
</ul><h2><strong>Anticipated Daily Routine:</strong></h2>
<ul><li>Open gates, start equipment up and commence with work at 7:30 am.</li>
